BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Edko Films
DESCRIPTION:After Wang Wei's daughter is kidnapped by a criminal network a
 nd he receives no help from the corrupt police\, Wei sets out to find her
  himself. His only ally is Navin\, a relentless journalist whose wife has
  mysteriously disappeared. Fueled by a furious vengeance\, the unlikely d
 uo ruthlessly battle the kidnappers in this explosive martial arts showdo
 wn.
